<HEADLINE> Tunis Stock Exchange Index Up </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TUNIS, August 31 (Xinhua) -- The Tunis Stock Exchange index
closed at 683.19 points Tuesday, up 0.38 percent from Monday's
finish.
</P>
<P>
A daily bulletin of the bourse said 146,040 shares changed
hands in 8,416 deals, and the turnover was 4,050,161 dinars (about
3.68 million U.S. dollars). 
</P>
