<HEADLINE> News Items from Asia-Pacific Desk of Xinhua </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, August 31 (Xinhua) -- Following are news items from
the Asia-Pacific Desk of Xinhua in Hong Kong Tuesday:

hke083130 -- Transactions at Manila Stock Exchange
hke083131 -- East Timor Police Request More Personnel
hke083132 -- Foreign Exchange Rates in Singapore
hke083133 -- Thai Bourse Down 6.21 Points
hka083134 -- Gold Price in Hong Kong Up
hka083135 -- Hang Seng China Enterprises Index Up
