---
</P>
<P>
ALMA ATA -- Foreign Minister Muratbek Imanaliyev said
Kyrgyzstan has enough force to wipe out armed Islamic invaders,
the Kyrgyz Telegraph Agency quoted him as saying on Monday.
</P>
<P>
Kyrgyz troops have successfully prevented the gunmen from
entering into its backland, Imanaliyev said. (Kyrgyzstan-Islamic
Gunman)
</P>
<P>
---
</P>
<P>
LUSAKA -- Some 46 founding members of the rebel Congolese Rally
for Democracy (RCD) signed a cease-fire agreement in Lusaka
Tuesday afternoon, raising hope that the year-long civil war in
Democratic Congo can be ended at long last.
</P>
<P>
