political visit, rather it is an "independent" visit.
</P>
<P>
The U.S. delegation said they make the visit to Iraq in order
to know what they can do to help lift the United Nations sanctions
imposed on Iraq following its 1990 invasion of Kuwait.
(BC-Iraq-US Congressional Delegation)
</P>
