York, King-Akerele held talks with Tete governor Virgilio Ferrao,
and they agreed that the initiative is essential for the
development of the areas.
</P>
<P>
"This program will be very useful, not only for the three
countries, but also for the remainder of the region", said
King-Akerele. 
