Earlier, No 7 Serena Williams advanced in a masterful and
efficient display of power tennis. Williams, 17, whipped Kimberly
Po 6-1, 6-0 in 49 minutes. Williams had five aces, pounded 26
winners and won nine of 10 points played at the net.
</P>
