totaled 2.7 billion HK dollars (346 million U.S. dollars) in 1997,
representing an average annual growth of over 21 percent since
1990," he noted.
</P>
<P>
Chan also highlighted the emergence of the Internet as a new
medium for advertising.
</P>
<P>
