intruded the Kutch area as a retaliatory move to the downing of a
Pakistani naval aircraft on August 10.
</P>
<P>
However, he asserted that any violation of Indian air or land
space will meet with the same response Indian forces had
demonstrated while evicting Pakistani intruders in Kargil.
