<HEADLINE> Israeli Negotiator Claims End to Talks Over Wye </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
JERUSALEM, September 1 (Xinhua) - Following his meeting with
Palestinian official, Israeli Prime Minister Ehud Barak's envoy
Gilad Sher said on Wednesday that from the Israeli respective, the
talks with the Palestinians over the implementation of the Wye
accord is over.
</P>
<P>
