the game against Switzerland four days later.
</P>
<P>
Currently, Belarus tailed in their group with two points from
five games while Italy are top with 14 from six matches followed
by Denmark and Switzerland with eight.
</P>
<P>
Following are the roster of the Belarus squad:
</P>
<P>
