Afanasenko (Dynamo Minsk), Vladimir Selkin (Gomel)
</P>
<P>
Defenders: Sergei Gurenko (AS Roma), Andrei Ostrovsky and
Sergei Shtanyuk (both Dynamo Moscow), Andrei Lavrik (Lokomotiv
Moscow), Alexander Lukhvich (Torpedo Moscow), Igor Tarlovsky(
Alania Vladikavkaz), Vladimir Sheleg (Sokol Saratov), Alexander
Khrapkovsky (Dynamo Minsk)
</P>
<P>
