Kulchiy (Dynamo Moscow), Vasily Baranov (Spartak Moscow),Alexander
Chaika (Alania Vladikavkaz), Vyacheslav Gerashchenko(Chernomorets
Novorossiisk), Vadim Skripchenko (BATE Borisov)
</P>
