<HEADLINE> Mexican Stocks Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MEXICO CITY, August 31 (Xinhua) -- The Mexican stock Exchange
closed down Tuesday with the Benchmark IPC index falling 87.93
points, or 1.70 percent, to 5,086.87.
</P>
<P>
